{
  "texts": [
    "Prompt engineering has emerged as a new sought-after skill and dozens of books are already available on the subject.",
    "The competition to produce more capable \"multimodal\" models, including smaller models, has increased.",
    "As of the time of this writing, new chatbot model releases included Pathways Language Model 2 (PaLM 2) that powered Google Bard (Ghahramani 2023) prior to Gemini (Pichai and Hassabis 2023), and Language Model for Many Applications (LLaMA) developed by Meta (Meta 2023).",
    "Future work will examine approaches towards achieving AGI, which may require innovations that go beyond simply continuing to increase the model size and training data."
  ]
}